WEBVTT


00:01:41.851 --> 00:01:47.857
THE EAST PALACE

00:01:50.318 --> 00:01:51.236
Crown Prince.

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:59.494
That spirit That spirit took my son!

00:02:00.870 --> 00:02:03.873
Your Majesty!

00:02:04.833 --> 00:02:06.334
Silence.

00:02:09.921 --> 00:02:11.881
Where is His Majesty?

00:02:18.221 --> 00:02:20.974
His Highness the Crown Prince went out alone at dawn?

00:02:21.057 --> 00:02:23.643
This will lead to greater chaos.

00:02:23.726 --> 00:02:26.813
The court must not be the first to be shaken.

00:02:26.896 --> 00:02:27.939
Chief Royal Secretary.

00:02:28.439 --> 00:02:29.691
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:02:31.818 --> 00:02:34.737
Proceed with the funeral rites at once.

00:02:35.822 --> 00:02:36.739
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:02:42.871 --> 00:02:44.164
Your Majesty.

00:02:45.456 --> 00:02:48.334
An incident has befallen the Crown Prince.

00:02:49.460 --> 00:02:51.004
Are you aware of it?

00:02:51.671 --> 00:02:52.797
I have heard.

00:02:57.886 --> 00:03:01.389
And yet, how can you remain so unperturbed?

00:03:01.472 --> 00:03:02.807
You may all withdraw.

00:03:02.891 --> 00:03:05.435
- Yes, Your Majesty. - Yes, Your Majesty.

00:03:09.105 --> 00:03:11.482
The Crown Princes are dying one after another.

00:03:11.566 --> 00:03:15.820
By that pond spirit, Jangpyeong, Yunpyeong, and the current Crown Prince--

00:03:15.904 --> 00:03:17.488
That is enough.

00:03:18.031 --> 00:03:19.991
There is no such thing as spirits.

00:03:20.491 --> 00:03:24.204
How could there be spirits in our Neo-Confucian royal house?

00:03:24.287 --> 00:03:25.622
Have you forgotten already?

00:03:25.705 --> 00:03:29.459
Thirty years ago, the Crown Princes died one after another, just as they do now!

00:03:29.542 --> 00:03:32.754
Yes. Thirty years have already passed.

00:03:32.837 --> 00:03:35.006
But this is not the same as it was then.

00:03:35.506 --> 00:03:39.385
My first and second sons died of illness.

00:03:40.136 --> 00:03:41.679
And the third Crown Prince,

00:03:42.180 --> 00:03:44.766
Being deeply tormented in mind,

00:03:45.683 --> 00:03:47.769
Chose to take his own life.

00:03:48.353 --> 00:03:55.151
Such things as spirits do not exist. Speak no more of them.

00:03:58.029 --> 00:04:02.533
Such talk would do Your Majesty no good, would it, Mother?

00:04:04.202 --> 00:04:07.038
If that is truly how you see it, Your Majesty

00:04:09.499 --> 00:04:11.793
Then just as you always have,

00:04:13.002 --> 00:04:15.171
Stay as you are and take no action.

00:04:16.047 --> 00:04:19.342
I shall see to the safety of the princes myself.

00:04:19.425 --> 00:04:22.887
I shall also find a way to ward off the spirit!

00:04:31.020 --> 00:04:35.400
His Highness the Crown Prince!

00:04:36.192 --> 00:04:38.861
Come back to us!

00:04:39.696 --> 00:04:42.532
Come back!

00:04:43.825 --> 00:04:46.911
Come back!

00:04:48.454 --> 00:04:51.708
Alas.

00:04:52.208 --> 00:04:55.628
Alas.

00:04:56.170 --> 00:04:59.257
Alas.

00:05:00.133 --> 00:05:03.845
Alas.

00:05:03.928 --> 00:05:06.973
Alas.

00:05:19.861 --> 00:05:23.156
Alas.

00:05:23.656 --> 00:05:27.452
Alas.

00:05:27.535 --> 00:05:29.245
Alas.

00:05:29.329 --> 00:05:30.830
Stop the wailing!

00:05:36.044 --> 00:05:37.128
Do you all truly believe

00:05:37.211 --> 00:05:41.466
That spirits could kill the sons of the King?

00:05:42.884 --> 00:05:47.638
That the late King and I lost our sons to spirits?

00:05:48.389 --> 00:05:50.892
And that the King fears spirits?

00:05:51.893 --> 00:05:55.229
What officials or subjects would ever follow such a king?

00:05:55.313 --> 00:05:57.857
- Your Majesty. - Your Majesty.

00:05:58.358 --> 00:06:01.444
Mere spirits cannot lay a hand on the royal bloodline.

00:06:02.153 --> 00:06:06.074
No one can threaten the royal authority

00:06:11.329 --> 00:06:13.247
Be it human or spirit.

00:06:30.807 --> 00:06:32.725
Do you truly believe

00:06:33.226 --> 00:06:35.353
The spirits can be subdued by that man?

00:06:35.937 --> 00:06:38.731
He is the most renowned shaman in the capital.

00:07:44.380 --> 00:07:48.593
I will eradicate the royal bloodline.

00:08:09.405 --> 00:08:11.657
Your Majesty, Prince Yeongan is

00:08:20.374 --> 00:08:22.543
What is the matter now, Prince Yeongan?

00:08:23.044 --> 00:08:23.920
Prince Yeongan!

00:08:24.420 --> 00:08:25.713
What has happened?

00:08:26.214 --> 00:08:29.550
Prince Yeongan has suddenly gone into a convulsion.

00:08:31.385 --> 00:08:34.055
Prince Yeongan.

00:08:37.225 --> 00:08:38.184
Prince Yeongan

00:08:42.605 --> 00:08:44.190
Did you see?

00:08:44.273 --> 00:08:45.858
Did you?

00:08:46.859 --> 00:08:49.529
I will take this one as well.

00:08:51.989 --> 00:08:56.160
Prince Yeongan! No! Please, no!

00:08:56.244 --> 00:08:57.370
Please stop!

00:09:04.877 --> 00:09:07.755
Please save Prince Yeongan, Your Majesty.

00:09:07.838 --> 00:09:11.467
I will wipe out every last seed of the East Palace!

00:09:17.515 --> 00:09:20.017
<i>What occurred 30 years ago</i>

00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:23.020
<i>is repeating itself within the palace.</i>

00:09:23.563 --> 00:09:25.940
<i>Therefore, I need you</i> <i>to come with me this time</i>

00:09:26.691 --> 00:09:28.859
<i>and bring this matter to an end.</i>

00:09:30.486 --> 00:09:35.241
This humble monk is old and frail and can no longer shoulder such a task.

00:09:35.741 --> 00:09:38.869
However, there is someone else who may serve in my stead.

00:09:39.745 --> 00:09:40.830
Who is it?

00:09:40.913 --> 00:09:43.207
A boy named Gu-cheon.

00:09:45.793 --> 00:09:48.462
His mother was a shaman.

00:09:48.546 --> 00:09:50.256
When she conceived a child,

00:09:50.339 --> 00:09:53.342
The deity she served grew angered and laid a curse upon her.

00:09:55.094 --> 00:10:00.099
<i>In her agony, she threw herself</i> <i>into the river with her child.</i>

00:10:01.976 --> 00:10:05.271
<i>Yet the mother, a shaman, died,</i>

00:10:05.771 --> 00:10:08.149
<i>and the child survived.</i>

00:10:09.066 --> 00:10:11.360
<i>The child had been underwater</i> <i>for over 15 minutes</i>

00:10:11.444 --> 00:10:14.322
<i>and should not have survived.</i>

00:10:15.281 --> 00:10:17.408
<i>Perhaps because he died</i> <i>and came back to life,</i>

00:10:17.908 --> 00:10:21.495
<i>he has seen spirits ever since.</i>

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:27.126
Gu-cheon.

00:10:28.544 --> 00:10:30.171
You little rascal, get up.

00:10:30.671 --> 00:10:32.089
Get up.

00:10:32.173 --> 00:10:34.175
Get up at once!

00:10:34.258 --> 00:10:37.470
Come now, get up!

00:10:41.015 --> 00:10:43.559
Have you gone senile

00:10:43.643 --> 00:10:45.811
In this temple of Buddha and the Mountain God?

00:10:46.312 --> 00:10:50.107
<i>Why do you keep sleeping here</i> <i>instead of your perfectly good room?</i>

00:10:50.191 --> 00:10:53.903
Things come out at night and torment me, so I sleep here.

00:10:54.403 --> 00:10:56.280
For heaven's sake.

00:10:57.323 --> 00:10:58.324
Gu-cheon,

00:10:58.824 --> 00:11:01.118
Someone of high standing has come to see you.

00:11:01.202 --> 00:11:04.288
- Come with me at once. - No. What would you have me do?

00:11:04.372 --> 00:11:06.624
Do not sleep the day away and earn your keep.

00:11:06.707 --> 00:11:08.167
With that one thing you can do--

00:11:08.250 --> 00:11:11.295
I told you I truly do not wish to do such work.

00:11:11.379 --> 00:11:12.672
A Buddhist earning his keep?

00:11:12.755 --> 00:11:15.466
- What a shameless monk. - What? Shameless?

00:11:15.549 --> 00:11:19.011
Fine. I have been wanting to quit this shameless monk life.

00:11:24.308 --> 00:11:26.560
You do not look well.

00:11:26.644 --> 00:11:28.229
Is something wrong?

00:11:29.271 --> 00:11:32.274
Worry about yourself. You look deathly pale.

00:11:32.358 --> 00:11:34.443
- Enough. - What do you want with me?

00:11:34.944 --> 00:11:37.988
I heard you can see spirits and even drive them out.

00:11:38.072 --> 00:11:41.409
Good grief, you must be telling the entire village.

00:11:42.201 --> 00:11:44.578
No wonder anyone and everyone comes to see me.

00:11:44.662 --> 00:11:48.082
- Gu-cheon! - There is a reason spirits torment people.

00:11:48.165 --> 00:11:50.126
It is because they did something foul.

00:11:50.209 --> 00:11:52.795
Stop bringing me people who stink of such foul deeds.

00:11:53.671 --> 00:11:55.506
Watch your tongue, you rascal.

00:11:58.259 --> 00:12:00.261
He says his child is ill.

00:12:00.344 --> 00:12:03.347
Afflicted by a spirit, he is in grave condition.

00:12:04.348 --> 00:12:07.685
What does that have to do with me?

00:12:08.644 --> 00:12:10.479
Do not summon me over such trifles.

00:12:10.980 --> 00:12:12.606
I am going to get some sleep.

00:12:12.690 --> 00:12:13.899
Gu-cheon!

00:12:17.319 --> 00:12:18.195
What?

00:12:18.779 --> 00:12:21.991
Do you see something in me?

00:12:22.074 --> 00:12:23.200
Your right hand.

00:12:24.618 --> 00:12:25.828
You cannot use it.

00:12:27.288 --> 00:12:28.581
Why is that?

00:12:28.664 --> 00:12:30.791
You have a bite mark left by a spirit.

00:12:31.292 --> 00:12:33.294
Seeing that the flesh tore away,

00:12:33.377 --> 00:12:35.463
A spirit of deep resentment has clung to you.

00:12:36.672 --> 00:12:38.382
If only you had lived better.

00:12:38.924 --> 00:12:40.676
Even so, it is none of my concern.

00:12:41.177 --> 00:12:42.970
I beg your pardon.

00:13:31.435 --> 00:13:33.103
I am at the palace.

00:13:39.693 --> 00:13:40.694
King

00:13:43.864 --> 00:13:46.158
- You may all withdraw. - Yes, Your Majesty.

00:13:51.497 --> 00:13:53.624
Do you know where this is?

00:13:54.500 --> 00:13:56.752
Yes, this is the palace.

00:13:57.253 --> 00:13:58.921
It is where Your Majesty resides.

00:13:59.547 --> 00:14:04.260
Yes, it is a vast, beautiful,

00:14:05.511 --> 00:14:06.971
And opulent residence.

00:14:11.767 --> 00:14:15.396
At this pond, the Crown Prince was bewitched by a spirit and died.

00:14:16.063 --> 00:14:19.233
It said, "I will wipe out every last seed of the East Palace."

00:14:19.316 --> 00:14:24.196
Even my one remaining young son is now on the brink of death. So

00:14:26.115 --> 00:14:27.992
I need you to ward off that spirit.

00:14:29.660 --> 00:14:31.579
What is the nature of that spirit?

00:14:31.662 --> 00:14:34.081
That is none of your concern. Can you do it?

00:14:34.665 --> 00:14:37.793
Can you find that spirit and get rid of it?

00:15:02.735 --> 00:15:04.695
It is no longer present.

00:15:04.778 --> 00:15:06.238
The spirit

00:15:07.114 --> 00:15:08.699
Has gone elsewhere.

00:15:11.118 --> 00:15:13.287
I will have to look at other places as well.

00:15:23.088 --> 00:15:24.131
Wait.

00:15:30.054 --> 00:15:31.472
You should stay here.

00:15:32.181 --> 00:15:33.599
What do you think you are doing?

00:15:34.934 --> 00:15:38.312
If those with strong energy are nearby, the spirit will flee,

00:15:38.812 --> 00:15:40.397
So I will go alone and see.

00:15:44.318 --> 00:15:45.819
Do not attempt anything foolish.

00:16:02.962 --> 00:16:06.006
That crazy, shameless monk sold me off to the palace.

00:16:07.132 --> 00:16:09.385
I cannot. I must not do this.

00:16:09.468 --> 00:16:12.388
No, wait!

00:16:16.433 --> 00:16:19.728
The Big Dipper lies that way, so this way!

00:16:26.652 --> 00:16:27.736
Good grief.

00:16:41.792 --> 00:16:45.170
Well my stomach hurt, so

00:16:49.508 --> 00:16:51.427
No, seriously

00:16:53.220 --> 00:16:55.139
This is unfair!

00:16:57.224 --> 00:16:59.518
I did not choose to enter the palace.

00:17:00.019 --> 00:17:02.062
However lowborn I may be

00:17:08.861 --> 00:17:10.279
Mark my words.

00:17:11.530 --> 00:17:13.574
If you attempt to flee again

00:17:15.743 --> 00:17:18.328
I will sever both your feet.

00:17:19.163 --> 00:17:22.291
If you tell others that you hunt spirits here,

00:17:22.875 --> 00:17:25.377
I will sever your jaw.

00:17:26.003 --> 00:17:29.298
If you fail to capture the spirit and my son is harmed,

00:17:29.798 --> 00:17:32.551
I will sever your head.

00:17:34.803 --> 00:17:38.724
They say that once you enter the palace, you leave only in death.

00:17:39.475 --> 00:17:40.809
That is what the palace is.

00:17:41.852 --> 00:17:44.271
If you wish to leave the palace alive,

00:17:45.022 --> 00:17:47.691
Then capture the spirit at once and get rid of it.

00:17:48.609 --> 00:17:51.528
If you do so, I will grant you whatever you wish.

00:17:52.571 --> 00:17:53.697
Do you understand?

00:18:00.454 --> 00:18:04.416
From this moment on, by royal command, you are a feng shui master of the palace.

00:18:06.043 --> 00:18:08.629
I will assign you someone who may be of use.

00:18:51.505 --> 00:18:53.048
You are hardly recognizable.

00:18:55.050 --> 00:18:56.677
It has been ten years.

00:18:57.302 --> 00:19:01.390
Do you know why I summoned you?

00:19:01.473 --> 00:19:05.060
You must have needed someone trustworthy to keep a secret.

00:19:07.563 --> 00:19:09.815
To save your dying son,

00:19:10.607 --> 00:19:12.943
You summoned your daughter, who was as good as dead.

00:19:15.571 --> 00:19:19.950
I see you still carry what happened to you as a child.

00:19:22.911 --> 00:19:24.163
How could that be?

00:19:25.998 --> 00:19:28.000
I am only glad

00:19:28.834 --> 00:19:30.544
To be of service to you, Father.

00:19:36.633 --> 00:19:39.386
<i>I have brought a spirit-catcher</i> <i>into the palace.</i>

00:19:40.804 --> 00:19:44.433
<i>Be my eyes and ears,</i> <i>and keep watch on him.</i>

00:19:46.059 --> 00:19:49.688
<i>Whether to entrust him with the task</i> <i>or put him to death,</i>

00:19:50.689 --> 00:19:52.858
<i>I will decide through you.</i>

00:20:01.575 --> 00:20:02.826
Is anyone here?

00:20:10.834 --> 00:20:13.754
"Someone who may be of use"? Who on earth is he assigning to me?

00:20:14.254 --> 00:20:16.256
I suppose he will send some fearsome men.

00:20:16.340 --> 00:20:18.800
There are fearsome men everywhere.

00:20:19.301 --> 00:20:20.802
For heaven's sake.

00:20:21.345 --> 00:20:22.638
That shameless monk

00:20:23.388 --> 00:20:24.598
Look here.

00:20:26.099 --> 00:20:27.142
Look here!

00:20:27.226 --> 00:20:28.602
Damn it.

00:20:31.188 --> 00:20:32.397
Who are you?

00:20:32.481 --> 00:20:33.941
Why do you not answer?

00:20:35.192 --> 00:20:36.818
Why do you open the door without

00:20:39.112 --> 00:20:41.990
His Majesty sent me to assist you.

00:20:43.116 --> 00:20:45.953
- What am I to do with someone like you? - Pardon?

00:20:46.036 --> 00:20:49.539
I clearly said to change my room first, not to send me useless people,

00:20:49.623 --> 00:20:50.791
Yet he pays no heed.

00:20:50.874 --> 00:20:53.085
I have not slept a wink all night.

00:20:53.168 --> 00:20:56.380
I am truly at my wits' end!

00:20:57.756 --> 00:21:01.260
You lose your temper the moment we meet. Do you have no manners?

00:21:02.386 --> 00:21:06.348
Your quarters were chosen to avoid prying eyes, so do not complain.

00:21:06.431 --> 00:21:07.349
Complain?

00:21:08.475 --> 00:21:10.060
Complain? Ridiculous.

00:21:10.560 --> 00:21:11.645
Look.

00:21:13.355 --> 00:21:15.565
Do you know why there is no one here?

00:21:16.483 --> 00:21:20.737
People keep dying here for no reason, do they?

00:21:20.821 --> 00:21:25.993
It is because all the Yin energy gathers

00:21:28.287 --> 00:21:30.163
And things like that come to dwell here.

00:21:30.747 --> 00:21:31.581
What?

00:21:33.917 --> 00:21:34.918
Ominous.

00:21:35.419 --> 00:21:38.922
What exactly is here?

00:21:42.634 --> 00:21:43.802
Oh dear.

00:21:44.970 --> 00:21:48.598
It must be comforting for you, seeing nothing at all.

00:21:49.266 --> 00:21:50.809
I will just go to sleep.

00:21:52.227 --> 00:21:56.106
- One cannot expect courtesy from a brute. - A brute?

00:21:56.189 --> 00:21:59.401
In any case, this is our first meeting.

00:21:59.484 --> 00:22:00.819
Let us exchange greetings.

00:22:02.446 --> 00:22:04.406
I am Saeng-gang, an inspecting court lady.

00:22:04.906 --> 00:22:07.492
They say you handle spirits as a shaman.

00:22:07.576 --> 00:22:09.661
A shaman? Nonsense. I do not even serve spirits.

00:22:09.745 --> 00:22:11.079
You are no shaman?

00:22:11.163 --> 00:22:13.790
- Then how will you hunt the pond spirit? - None of your concern, so

00:22:17.711 --> 00:22:19.463
Just do as I tell you.

00:22:21.965 --> 00:22:26.345
That thing on the ceiling kept me awake, so I will sleep for now.

00:22:30.307 --> 00:22:32.559
- Much to be done. - What is the matter with you?

00:22:33.977 --> 00:22:35.270
Come out!

00:22:35.354 --> 00:22:36.772
There is no time to lose.

00:22:44.404 --> 00:22:46.740
He must be the feng shui master.

00:22:47.324 --> 00:22:49.451
- Where? - The one who just passed by.

00:22:50.786 --> 00:22:52.621
Walk straight.

00:22:53.830 --> 00:22:55.999
You are in the palace as a feng shui master.

00:22:56.083 --> 00:22:57.793
Mind your conduct.

00:22:58.710 --> 00:23:01.671
I know nothing about feng shui.

00:23:02.589 --> 00:23:03.757
Good grief.

00:23:09.388 --> 00:23:10.472
You insolent wench.

00:23:10.555 --> 00:23:13.850
How dare you raise your head and look me in the eye.

00:23:13.934 --> 00:23:15.477
Have you no manners?

00:23:19.398 --> 00:23:22.943
My apologies, ma'am. I am a court maid from the inspectorate.

00:23:23.485 --> 00:23:27.364
By His Majesty's command, I brought a feng shui master to Prince Yeongan.

00:23:30.575 --> 00:23:34.830
Leave. Her Majesty the Queen Dowager has ordered that no one be admitted today.

00:23:38.875 --> 00:23:39.876
Goodness.

00:23:39.960 --> 00:23:43.422
After all that talk about manners, you came away with nothing but a scolding.

00:23:43.505 --> 00:23:44.673
Good grief.

00:23:47.676 --> 00:23:51.721
Well, have you had a look around? No sign of the pond spirit in the room?

00:23:51.805 --> 00:23:54.683
How would I know? It is not as if I can see through walls.

00:23:54.766 --> 00:23:56.309
Then what exactly can you do?

00:23:56.393 --> 00:23:57.352
Please!

00:23:57.853 --> 00:24:01.815
Why are you taking the scolding out on me? For goodness' sake.

00:24:01.898 --> 00:24:04.526
You should at least feel some presence.

00:24:12.868 --> 00:24:14.870
His Majesty has sent a feng shui master.

00:24:17.539 --> 00:24:19.166
A feng shui master?

00:24:21.293 --> 00:24:24.004
What on earth is His Majesty thinking?

00:24:24.087 --> 00:24:26.840
It is said that he is staying in the quarters

00:24:26.923 --> 00:24:28.884
At the far east end of the East Palace.

00:24:29.384 --> 00:24:30.510
What?

00:24:31.136 --> 00:24:33.722
Is that not the place long plagued by unnatural deaths?

00:24:34.556 --> 00:24:39.186
Yes, Your Majesty. It was left vacant after so many sudden deaths at night.

00:24:42.522 --> 00:24:43.857
A feng shui master.

00:24:44.357 --> 00:24:46.902
What kind of man is he?

00:24:51.698 --> 00:24:52.991
Are you all right?

00:24:59.080 --> 00:25:00.332
Have you lost your mind?

00:25:00.415 --> 00:25:03.919
You carry a great deal of Yang energy. A rare constitution, indeed.

00:25:11.927 --> 00:25:14.471
His Majesty's judgment must have clouded

00:25:14.971 --> 00:25:17.265
To entrust such a task to someone like you.

00:25:17.766 --> 00:25:20.477
He assigned you to me because His Majesty does not trust me.

00:25:20.560 --> 00:25:21.770
I am here

00:25:22.270 --> 00:25:25.565
Only because he threatened my life.

00:25:26.066 --> 00:25:29.319
Damn, that bastard. He locks people up just because he has some power.

00:25:30.487 --> 00:25:32.322
Are you speaking of His Majesty?

00:25:32.948 --> 00:25:34.491
- That is high treason! - What?

00:25:34.574 --> 00:25:37.160
I meant Chil-bok from the temple I lived in.

00:25:38.495 --> 00:25:41.039
Heavens. Just my luck.

00:25:43.917 --> 00:25:47.212
How long do you intend to keep walking?

00:25:47.712 --> 00:25:49.714
Are you out for a stroll?

00:25:52.133 --> 00:25:53.552
This will not do.

00:25:53.635 --> 00:25:55.804
Let us go to the pond where the spirit appears.

00:25:55.887 --> 00:25:57.264
There is no need.

00:25:57.889 --> 00:26:00.475
I got there, and the spirit had already moved on.

00:26:01.017 --> 00:26:04.354
It is not as if spirits are bound to one place the way gwi-mae are.

00:26:05.605 --> 00:26:06.731
Gwi-mae?

00:26:07.774 --> 00:26:08.817
What is that?

00:26:09.317 --> 00:26:12.279
For goodness' sake. This is so bothersome.

00:26:13.738 --> 00:26:16.199
Who would know anything about spirits?

00:26:17.158 --> 00:26:21.037
Stop complaining and explain it to me. I can start learning now.

00:26:22.289 --> 00:26:24.040
A gwi-mae

00:26:24.541 --> 00:26:27.043
Does not come from a human death, as spirits do.

00:26:27.544 --> 00:26:29.504
It forms when sinister forces of nature

00:26:29.588 --> 00:26:33.925
Or the energy from human ill will gather in one place.

00:26:34.009 --> 00:26:36.386
There was one on the ceiling of my room earlier

00:26:38.054 --> 00:26:39.431
And another one over there.

00:26:44.185 --> 00:26:46.813
<i>It has no soul,</i> <i>so it cannot be driven out like a spirit.</i>

00:26:46.896 --> 00:26:48.607
<i>It is more troublesome to handle.</i>

00:26:49.107 --> 00:26:52.235
<i>They torment people</i> <i>with darkness in their hearts</i>

00:26:52.736 --> 00:26:53.987
<i>and bewitch them.</i>

00:26:58.908 --> 00:26:59.993
Let us go.

00:27:00.076 --> 00:27:02.037
It is best to avoid them.

00:27:08.585 --> 00:27:11.504
Then is the pond spirit a gwi-mae as well?

00:27:12.005 --> 00:27:14.924
Gwi-mae do not hold grudges against humans.

00:27:15.008 --> 00:27:17.552
- It is most likely a won-gwi. - A won-gwi?

00:27:17.636 --> 00:27:20.096
- What is a won-gwi? - Good grief.

00:27:24.225 --> 00:27:27.937
Among the many kinds of spirits, common-gwi are souls lingering in regret,

00:27:28.021 --> 00:27:30.148
Unable to pass on to the afterlife.

00:27:30.857 --> 00:27:33.068
They cause no real harm.

00:27:33.902 --> 00:27:36.863
Won-gwi are the souls of those who died bearing deep resentment.

00:27:36.946 --> 00:27:40.283
They torment the one who caused their resentment.

00:27:40.367 --> 00:27:42.452
As the resentment grows and takes form,

00:27:42.535 --> 00:27:45.705
It weighs down the soul and binds it to the earth,

00:27:45.789 --> 00:27:47.165
Keeping it from passing on.

00:27:51.336 --> 00:27:53.588
Only by getting rid of that mass of resentment

00:27:55.173 --> 00:27:57.884
Can the soul bound to the earth be released to pass on.

00:27:58.885 --> 00:28:00.929
And even that will be no easy feat.

00:28:03.807 --> 00:28:07.477
The pond spirit Prince Yeongan The pond spirit

00:28:11.481 --> 00:28:14.150
Prince Yeongan is being tormented by a spirit.

00:28:15.318 --> 00:28:18.029
I cannot believe she turned away people sent by His Majesty.

00:28:18.571 --> 00:28:20.990
Does the Queen Dowager have any sense at all?

00:28:21.491 --> 00:28:23.743
Huh? Well, well.

00:28:24.369 --> 00:28:27.747
You speak ill of the Queen Dowager? You said it was treason for me to do so.

00:28:31.126 --> 00:28:34.879
More importantly, why tear up all the perfectly good sheets?

00:28:35.547 --> 00:28:36.673
None of your concern.

00:28:38.842 --> 00:28:40.635
You seem quite at ease.

00:28:40.719 --> 00:28:43.930
We must see Prince Yeongan to banish the spirit, yet you seem unconcerned.

00:28:44.013 --> 00:28:46.474
Of course I am concerned.

00:28:46.558 --> 00:28:51.020
If I fail to save the son of His Majesty, I will be the one to die.

00:28:51.104 --> 00:28:52.731
It even leaves me sleepless at night.

00:28:53.231 --> 00:28:54.315
What I mean is,

00:28:54.399 --> 00:28:57.819
Is it not pitiful that the child is tormented by such a grotesque thing?

00:28:57.902 --> 00:29:00.488
I do not even know this child. Why should it concern me?

00:29:02.115 --> 00:29:03.950
How can you think only of yourself?

00:29:04.451 --> 00:29:07.912
If you have the time, look into that pond spirit instead.

00:29:07.996 --> 00:29:10.623
Who it was in life and what grudge it bears.

00:29:10.707 --> 00:29:13.293
Only then can I get rid of the pond spirit.

00:29:13.376 --> 00:29:16.087
It will be difficult. Even if they know, they will not speak.

00:29:16.171 --> 00:29:18.673
Then go fetch a peach tree branch.

00:29:18.757 --> 00:29:20.049
One that grows eastward.

00:29:21.551 --> 00:29:24.804
- What for? - You never simply say yes.

00:29:26.306 --> 00:29:27.599
Fetch it at once.

00:29:30.310 --> 00:29:31.144
This man, truly

00:29:33.188 --> 00:29:35.356
Ask again, with proper respect!

00:29:36.024 --> 00:29:37.275
Be quick!

00:29:37.358 --> 00:29:39.527
Assist me? Nonsense. She does not know a thing.

00:29:42.989 --> 00:29:45.658
Why does it have to be a branch growing eastward?

00:29:53.583 --> 00:29:55.794
Here. This should do, should it not?

00:29:57.253 --> 00:29:59.881
I have heard that peach trees drive away spirits.

00:30:00.632 --> 00:30:01.674
Well done.

00:30:03.301 --> 00:30:07.388
- How will you ward off spirits with that? - Oh, that feels good.

00:30:09.724 --> 00:30:11.184
Much better.

00:30:17.982 --> 00:30:21.236
- I almost died trying to reach it. - All this just to scratch your back?

00:30:28.326 --> 00:30:30.328
<i>I submit this report to you, Father.</i>

00:30:31.079 --> 00:30:33.373
<i>You may set aside your concern</i>

00:30:33.456 --> 00:30:36.668
<i>that he might uncover anything</i> <i>about the pond spirit</i>

00:30:36.751 --> 00:30:40.004
<i>because he is doing nothing at all.</i>

00:30:40.588 --> 00:30:43.550
<i>He stays in his room all day,</i> <i>speaking only of sleep.</i>

00:30:52.433 --> 00:30:56.271
- Why does this keep happening? - How many times has this happened?

00:30:56.354 --> 00:30:59.023
I know. The rumors of a spirit in the East Palace seem to be true.

00:30:59.107 --> 00:31:00.191
So it seems.

00:31:00.275 --> 00:31:02.569
Prince Yeongan cannot take even rice gruel.

00:31:02.652 --> 00:31:05.488
- Exactly. They say he is worse this time. - Pardon me.

00:31:07.282 --> 00:31:09.325
What is going on?

00:31:15.832 --> 00:31:17.917
What on earth is happening to him?

00:31:20.753 --> 00:31:22.422
- Prince Yeongan! - What ails him?

00:31:22.505 --> 00:31:24.507
Please come to your senses, Prince Yeongan!

00:31:25.216 --> 00:31:28.344
- Do something at once! - Prince Yeongan.

00:31:28.970 --> 00:31:31.598
- Come to your senses. - Is he truly possessed by a spirit?

00:31:32.849 --> 00:31:34.809
What on earth should we do?

00:31:41.524 --> 00:31:43.067
Prince Yeongan is gravely ill.

00:31:49.240 --> 00:31:51.701
- Already? - What will you do?

00:32:00.835 --> 00:32:02.253
No other choice, then.

00:32:11.346 --> 00:32:13.348
What are you going to do with it

00:32:20.521 --> 00:32:23.358
So are you going to Prince Yeongan?

00:32:23.441 --> 00:32:25.318
You should stay here. It is not safe.

00:32:32.158 --> 00:32:36.204
You never listen, do you? I told you not to follow.

00:32:36.287 --> 00:32:38.081
I said you must go to Prince Yeongan.

00:32:38.164 --> 00:32:41.084
That is why I am here. I am going to Prince Yeongan.

00:32:41.167 --> 00:32:42.710
What on earth are you trying to do?

00:32:42.794 --> 00:32:46.047
I have no choice in letting you see me like this,

00:32:46.130 --> 00:32:49.884
But you must not tell anyone what I am about to do.

00:32:54.722 --> 00:32:57.141
Why are you putting blood on the branch?

00:32:57.225 --> 00:32:59.811
So I may bring it into the other world.

00:33:00.311 --> 00:33:01.771
The other world? You mean

00:33:03.272 --> 00:33:04.399
The Realm of Gwi.

00:33:06.192 --> 00:33:07.068
The Realm of Gwi

00:33:07.151 --> 00:33:08.778
I may not come out of the water.

00:33:10.780 --> 00:33:14.158
- Even then, do not pull me up. - Are you telling me to let you die?

00:33:14.242 --> 00:33:17.328
Yes. That is how I reach the Realm of Gwi.

00:33:19.330 --> 00:33:21.165
Oh, right. Since you followed me

00:33:26.629 --> 00:33:30.800
Spirits may be listening. Come closer so we can speak quietly.

00:33:45.356 --> 00:33:49.736
I lack Yang energy, so it would be best for me to take something of yours.

00:33:57.368 --> 00:33:58.453
Well

00:34:01.372 --> 00:34:02.915
You should go now.

00:34:04.500 --> 00:34:06.377
Remember what I told you to do.

00:34:08.796 --> 00:34:09.881
Look here.

00:37:47.348 --> 00:37:48.766
What should we do?

00:37:49.267 --> 00:37:51.143
What should we do about this?

00:37:52.770 --> 00:37:54.897
- Prince Yeongan! - Prince Yeongan.

00:38:03.656 --> 00:38:05.533
Prince Prince Yeongan!

00:38:22.049 --> 00:38:25.386
<i>"I shall burn your vessel,</i> <i>shrouded in darkness."</i>

00:38:59.670 --> 00:39:00.963
- Your Highness! - Prince Yeongan!

00:39:01.047 --> 00:39:03.424
- Lady Jang, summon - Please come to your senses!

00:39:03.507 --> 00:39:05.426
- Summon the physician! - Yes, ma'am.

00:39:31.369 --> 00:39:34.372
If Prince Yeongan shows any signs of waking,

00:39:34.872 --> 00:39:36.999
Let it see your blood.

00:39:37.583 --> 00:39:39.168
<i>The window will be brief.</i>

00:40:34.098 --> 00:40:35.516
I knew it would not work,

00:40:35.599 --> 00:40:37.685
Not knowing the nature of that spirit.

00:40:57.997 --> 00:40:59.540
He truly is here.

00:41:11.760 --> 00:41:12.845
Who are you?

00:41:14.054 --> 00:41:17.099
What grudge drives you to kill the royal bloodline?

00:44:18.822 --> 00:44:22.117
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang

